sigma_analysis_results.rule_title: Potential Data Stealing Via Chromium Headless Debugging
sigma_analysis_results.rule_description: Detects chromium based browsers starting in headless and debugging mode and pointing to a user profile. This could be a sign of data stealing or remote control
